  "content": "<p data-pid=\"2gIyl2oG\">本系列专门介绍 SuperMemo 的各种小技巧和绕坑方法。</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/797904700\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">SuperMemo tips</a><p data-pid=\"XHBf_3Om\">这是因为从 epub 导入的内容，图片路径是相对于 epub 文件的路径，如下图所示：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-717bfb982f96bca7d9b647fef72c7279_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2196\" data-rawheight=\"394\" data-original-token=\"v2-717bfb982f96bca7d9b647fef72c7279\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b702a787a275127d1925f1cdb831dd0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2196\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-717bfb982f96bca7d9b647fef72c7279_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2196&#39; height=&#39;394&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2196\" data-rawheight=\"394\" data-original-token=\"v2-717bfb982f96bca7d9b647fef72c7279\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8b702a787a275127d1925f1cdb831dd0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2196\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-717bfb982f96bca7d9b647fef72c7279_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-717bfb982f96bca7d9b647fef72c7279_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c343216f7de01b639f5385fd37ce2e8e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1244\" data-rawheight=\"534\" data-original-token=\"v2-c343216f7de01b639f5385fd37ce2e8e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-178d7da55f218c99e2c1ae9ffb529abe_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1244\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c343216f7de01b639f5385fd37ce2e8e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1244&#39; height=&#39;534&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1244\" data-rawheight=\"534\" data-original-token=\"v2-c343216f7de01b639f5385fd37ce2e8e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-178d7da55f218c99e2c1ae9ffb529abe_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1244\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c343216f7de01b639f5385fd37ce2e8e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c343216f7de01b639f5385fd37ce2e8e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"eE9JlsJY\">所以解决方案也不难，把 images 文件夹移动到 <code>sm18/systems/elements/</code> 这个路径下就行了</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b2f1d78ac59f168e0fc9ae0971e8af3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1108\" data-rawheight=\"362\" data-original-token=\"v2-7b2f1d78ac59f168e0fc9ae0971e8af3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-20c61595e89d872d8015802c6a7f3ad0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1108\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-7b2f1d78ac59f168e0fc9ae0971e8af3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1108&#39; height=&#39;362&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1108\" data-rawheight=\"362\" data-original-token=\"v2-7b2f1d78ac59f168e0fc9ae0971e8af3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-20c61595e89d872d8015802c6a7f3ad0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1108\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-7b2f1d78ac59f168e0fc9ae0971e8af3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b2f1d78ac59f168e0fc9ae0971e8af3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"bvds04Io\">效果展示（如果不行就重开一下 supermemo）：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-300e9149b31a992adc9cefb2ba92ae01_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1206\" data-rawheight=\"920\" data-original-token=\"v2-300e9149b31a992adc9cefb2ba92ae01\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d92d6369ff3dfe999cbe622b6256257_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1206\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-300e9149b31a992adc9cefb2ba92ae01_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1206&#39; height=&#39;920&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1206\" data-rawheight=\"920\" data-original-token=\"v2-300e9149b31a992adc9cefb2ba92ae01\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8d92d6369ff3dfe999cbe622b6256257_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1206\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-300e9149b31a992adc9cefb2ba92ae01_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-300e9149b31a992adc9cefb2ba92ae01_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"j_tvMo9Z\">当然这个方法有个问题，就是如果你有好几本 epub 要导入，那么图片名称和路径会冲突，然后导致相互覆盖。这种时候，我建议用 vscode 批量改一下路径，然后把 images 文件夹的名称和路径改成一样的，比如都改成 xxx_images，也就是类似命名空间的思路。</p><p data-pid=\"nT59RVpM\">更多和图片路径相关的内容，可以看这篇回答：</p><a href=\"http://www.zhihu.com/answer/2371762689\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-753e1e8b4790e03f234aea88d8b06e03_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"786\" data-image-height=\"702\" class=\"internal\">关于Supermemo18里的图片保存路径的几个疑惑？</a><p data-pid=\"9whmqOYL\">更多 SuperMemo 教程请见：</p><a href=\"http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/374403541\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1a8d0bb90f07e4147c5e401dda14d280_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1780\" data-image-height=\"1100\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：渐进学习专栏导读</a><p></p>",
